{"tid":1335472,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢都會用iphone嘅人請入","createTime":"2019-07-20T13:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T19:55:25.000Z","uid":8550,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8499db263abf2bdfd543cf6bcf4932c4c87c3278","tid":1335472,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"有時同fd落bar飲大咗 唔想俾fd用自己隻手指開電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n咁原來iphone有個飲醉酒功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niphone <strong>連續撳5下power 掣</strong> 之後會強制變做要用密碼解鎖 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個畫面就代表生效：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gANPHtr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgANPHtr.png&h=ce932bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但記住<br />\n<br />\n只會 temporary 生效一次<br />\n<br />\n你個醉酒mode開咗之後用password 解鎖 下一次解鎖會變返touch/face id<br />\n<br />\n之後想用返呢個function就要重新撳多5下</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗冇人會想俾人解鎖自己部電話<br />\n飲大咗記得小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a56c221e56f9e3de641a90af2ff4fe46bfc40b6","tid":1335472,"uid":162811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd2da8b0ecbb02d787d5d9a52adf0ae840797b0f","tid":1335472,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a56c221e56f9e3de641a90af2ff4fe46bfc40b6","tid":1335472,"uid":162811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1487c2470fb1779e8ec0690dcd18d54fa5c5a4dc","tid":1335472,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e0fc6fb73dcced0f52215bbee5ba8e4f00b2b47","tid"